- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a game semantics for type theory, which is a logical system. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the interpretation of a programming language (intuitionistic type theory) using game semantics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of dependent product and dependent sum, which are concepts used in some machine learning models. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the interpretation of computational equalities. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses the interpretation of a type theory with Id-types, which can have implications for the complexity of computations.
